often eliminating the need

00:01:09.220 --> 00:01:10.630 align:middle line:90%
to turn to pharmaceuticals.

00:01:10.630 --> 00:01:13.160 align:middle line:84%
And wow, this is
really good news

00:01:13.160 --> 00:01:14.330 align:middle line:90%
for an awful lot of people.

00:01:14.330 --> 00:01:16.930 align:middle line:84%
And you have changed
the lives of how many?

00:01:16.930 --> 00:01:18.520 align:middle line:84%
hundreds, thousands
of people by now?

00:01:18.520 --> 00:01:19.386 align:middle line:84%
>>TRUDY SCOTT:
Thousands of people.

00:01:19.386 --> 00:01:19.820 align:middle line:90%
