00:02:50.460 --> 00:02:50.940 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Yeah.

00:02:50.940 --> 00:02:51.730 align:middle line:84%
>>SCOTT: The other
thing that I really

00:02:51.730 --> 00:02:53.630 align:middle line:84%
