tolerate feeling bad.

00:02:55.667 --> 00:02:57.250 align:middle line:84%
You know, some people
have felt so bad

00:02:57.250 --> 00:03:01.092 align:middle line:84%
for so long they don't remember
what it felt like to feel good.

00:03:01.092 --> 00:03:02.800 align:middle line:84%
