as a 10, anxiety

00:03:14.030 --> 00:03:17.190 align:middle line:84%
as an 8, perfectionism,
controlling,

00:03:17.190 --> 00:03:18.514 align:middle line:90%
all of these, depression.

00:03:18.514 --> 00:03:19.930 align:middle line:84%
