people just being

00:03:32.130 --> 00:03:33.965 align:middle line:84%
like that their whole lives
and not even realizing it.

00:03:33.965 --> 00:03:34.400 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: They've accepted it.

00:03:34.400 --> 00:03:35.200 align:middle line:90%
>>SCOTT: Exactly.

00:03:35.200 --> 00:03:37.900 align:middle line:84%
But there's the other issue
where people are getting older,

00:03:37.900 --> 00:03:39.436 align:middle line:84%
maybe a woman going
into menopause.

00:03:39.436 --> 00:03:41.060 align:middle line:84%
And they just think,
well, it's normal.

00:03:41.060 --> 00:03:41.850 align:middle line:90%
My mom had it.

00:03:41.850 --> 00:03:42.860 align:middle line:90%
My grandmother had it.

00:03:42.860 --> 00:03:43.500 align:middle line:90%
I've got it.

00:03:43.500 --> 00:03:44.796 align:middle line:90%
I just have to put up with it.

00:03:44.796 --> 00:03:45.670 align:middle line:90%
And we don't have to.

00:03:45.670 --> 00:03:47.070 align:middle line:90%
We can actually change it.

00:03:47.070 --> 00:03:49.400 align:middle line:84%
And using food and nutrients
are just so powerful.

