the side of the cliff face.

00:04:30.630 --> 00:04:32.930 align:middle line:84%
And we actually met
in the mountains.

00:04:32.930 --> 00:04:34.600 align:middle line:84%
And we got married
and had our honeymoon

00:04:34.600 --> 00:04:35.900 align:middle line:90%
