my first panic attack.

00:04:53.700 --> 00:04:54.889 align:middle line:90%
I had come back from work.

00:04:54.889 --> 00:04:56.680 align:middle line:84%
I was actually working
in corporate America

00:04:56.680 --> 00:04:58.360 align:middle line:90%
