when I talk about this.

00:05:09.810 --> 00:05:11.100 align:middle line:90%
Because it was so terrifying.

00:05:11.100 --> 00:05:11.370 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Yes.

00:05:11.370 --> 00:05:13.411 align:middle line:84%
>>SCOTT: And I really
thought I was going to die.

00:05:13.411 --> 00:05:15.310 align:middle line:90%
It was just so, so scary.

00:05:15.310 --> 00:05:17.351 align:middle line:84%
And that galvanized
me into thinking

00:05:17.351 --> 00:05:19.850 align:middle line:84%
there's got to be something
that I've got to do about it now

00:05:19.850 --> 00:05:21.340 align:middle line:84%
because I'd had
the panic attack.

00:05:21.340 --> 00:05:22.890 align:middle line:84%
